    code: | 
        import numpy as np
        sr = 44100
        f0 = 220
        t = np.arange(sr*2)/sr
        decay = np.exp(-2*t)
        y = np.zeros_like(t)
        y += np.cos(2*np.pi*f0*t)*decay # Fundamental frequency
